data.text: @tyrone345345 As self hating as we are taught to be by the centuries of oppression and racist propaganda of Europeans who declared war on all things Afrocentric it’s funny to see how dissatisfied and self hating the most xenophobic and Eurocentric societies are. Poisoned by their own medicine.
